data-id=\"62faad0f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A new organisation run with donations and volunteer hours. Its goal is to support local authorities that have declared climate &amp; ecological emergencies and help them with their action plans, by providing information about best practice and a network where local authorities, activists, NGOs, business and local communities can work together.<\/p>\n<p>Current focus is a database of UK Local Authority climate &amp; ecological emergency declarations and action plans, to help interested parties quickly identify best practice. &#8220;We are also bringing together resources local authorities can use to deliver on their commitments, including a check list of what makes a good action plan&#8221;.<\/p>\n<p>They work with Councillors and officers as well as individual activists and NGO\u2019s including Friends of the Earth, Centre for Alternative Technology, Ashden, My Society, XR. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.climateemergency.uk\/\">https:\/\/www.climateemergency.uk\/<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-4b455772 elementor-reverse-tablet elementor-reverse-mobile elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"4b455772\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-49796185\" data-id=\"49796185\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-286d7079 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"286d7079\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Database of climate emergency declarations and action plans <\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5b27fd1b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5b27fd1b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Developed by ClimateEmergency.uk and mySociety, with input from a range of council climate officers, climate specialists, researchers, and journalists.<\/p><ul><li>Search for a phrase &#8211; Across all climate action plans in our database.<\/li><li>Find your council\u2019s action plan &#8211; Enter your postcode<\/li><li>Browse and compare all <strong>409 councils!<\/strong><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-533e7e0d elementor-align-justify elementor-widget__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"533e7e0d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-md\" href=\"https:\/\/data.climateemergency.uk\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Enter Database<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-a42ab0a\" data-id=\"a42ab0a\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a081156 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1a081156\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"450\" height=\"229\" src=\"https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/ClimateEmergencyDatabase.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-5027\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/ClimateEmergencyDatabase.png 450w, https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/ClimateEmergencyDatabase-300x153.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-43c52699 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"43c52699\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-5247f783\" data-id=\"5247f783\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7de8314b elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"7de8314b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/d