%20for%20a%20green%20recovery_refresh_Dec%202020_1.pdf\">Download PDF<\/a><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-262ed423 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"262ed423\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-4cc66d26\" data-id=\"4cc66d26\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-78779604 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"78779604\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-27a2cb62 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"27a2cb62\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-wider\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8c47a0d\" data-id=\"8c47a0d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f2ff5df elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5f2ff5df\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"western\">Friends of the Earth UK &#8211; Climate Action Groups<\/h2><p>A few years back FoE decided to set up the chain of \u2018Climate Action groups\u2019 which would include a wider group of people than FoE with the idea that anyone could set up and register a group. For the project, FoE provide a variety of resources. See:<strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/takeclimateaction.uk\/resources\">Take Climate Action<\/a>.<\/strong><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-39020aa9 elementor-reverse-tablet elementor-reverse-mobile elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"39020aa9\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-310c64f3\" data-id=\"310c64f3\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c9b4b52 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7c9b4b52\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Ideas and Examples for Ealing<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-76a34c0c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"76a34c0c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Put a Climate Change link on Council\u2019s home page, e.g. as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.scambs.gov.uk\/\">South Cambridgeshire District Council<\/a> do.<\/p><p>Add a link on the Council website to <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.imperial.ac.uk\/stories\/climate-action\">9 things you can do about climate change<\/a> <\/strong>(by The Grantham Institute at Imperial College).<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-3ba4b71\" data-id=\"3ba4b71\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5dd593f9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"5dd593f9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"542\" src=\"https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Grantham9ThingsToDo.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-5035\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Grantham9ThingsToDo.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Grantham9ThingsToDo-300x163.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ealingfoe.org.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/06\/Grantham9ThingsToDo-768x416.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-7c0d2795 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"7c0d2795\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor